1SCTのpriceの算出方法
priceAtPurchaseの配列を作成=[102,3939,144,339,554,2940,5555]
priceNow =[102,3939,144,339,554,2940,5555]

for文で回す
ChangeRate = priceANativeTokenNow/priceAtPurchase 
PartOfNowANativeTokenPrice = priceAtPurchase * ChangeRate
7つのPartOfNowANativeTokenPriceを合計して7でわる！

